{"text_id":51149,"tokens":["In"," today","'","s"," fast","-","paced"," and"," competitive"," academic"," world",","," the"," debate"," surrounding"," the"," requirement"," for"," students"," to"," participate"," in"," extracurricular"," activities"," after"," regular"," school"," hours"," has"," become"," increasingly"," relevant","."," While"," proponents"," argue"," that"," such"," a"," requirement"," fosters"," teamwork",","," leadership"," skills",","," and"," time"," management",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," mandatory"," participation"," in"," extracurricular"," activities"," is"," both"," unnecessary"," and"," detrimental"," to"," students","'"," overall"," well","-","being",".","\n\n","First"," and"," foremost",","," requiring"," students"," to"," participate"," in"," extracurricular"," activities"," after"," school"," can"," be"," overwhelming"," and"," stressful","."," Many"," students"," already"," have"," packed"," schedules",","," balancing"," academic"," respon","sibilities"," with"," social"," and"," personal"," commitments","."," Adding"," the"," pressure"," of"," extracurricular"," activities"," can"," lead"," to"," burnout",","," decreased"," motivation",","," and"," a"," decline"," in"," overall"," performance","."," Furthermore",","," this"," requirement"," can"," stifle"," creativity"," and"," individuality",","," as"," students"," are"," forced"," to"," conform"," to"," a"," predetermined"," mold",","," rather"," than"," exploring"," their"," unique"," interests"," and"," passions",".","\n\n","Additionally",","," the"," concept"," of"," mandatory"," participation"," in"," extracurricular"," activities"," raises"," concerns"," about"," equity"," and"," accessibility","."," Not"," all"," students"," have"," equal"," access"," to"," resources",","," facilities",","," or"," support"," networks",","," which"," can"," disproportion","ately"," affect"," marginalized"," or"," under","privileged"," groups","."," Such"," requirements"," can"," e